{
  "id": "RAW_7112ea",
  "title": "聊聊 Gemini 2.0 最近 3 个超级酷的新功能，Google 有点被低估了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/WdK2a5kByZWlOD5QeYB0Mw",
  "date": "2025-03-17 19:24:18",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google最近的动作真的多。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">感觉就是趁着OpenAI存粮打完了，疯狂的撒豆子一样往外面撒更新。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天晚上11点多，他们又发了一个关于Gemini的更新（其实功能礼拜天就上了，我也不知道他们为啥今天才发推文）。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1792294807370185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"597\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186049\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6751994f-b972-4957-a800-5a72c794ad00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6751994f-b972-4957-a800-5a72c794ad00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是这个东西。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6707317073170732\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"574\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186050\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ccdbfc83-8c9d-4278-1a7f-8e7cce119300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ccdbfc83-8c9d-4278-1a7f-8e7cce119300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这玩意，他会根据你的过往的所有Google搜索记录，来让模型更懂你，给你更加个性化的搜索的回答。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后就是上周五，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Google又发了Deep Research的更新</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，现在，底座换成了Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking，基座比之前的1.5Pro能力还是强太多了。而且，是100w token的上下文。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8400673400673401\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"594\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186051\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d215b2a5-6470-4090-438a-510eccef7300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d215b2a5-6470-4090-438a-510eccef7300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再就是上周四，几乎全网火爆的Gemini 2.0原生多模态，被玩出了各种花来。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1178451178451179\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"594\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186048\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01d75d3b-9ee1-49c9-12af-cc9748eec100/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01d75d3b-9ee1-49c9-12af-cc9748eec100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更别提同样在上周开源的Gemma&nbsp;3，以27B超小尺寸击败了DeepSeek v3、o3-mini等等。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6361111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186052\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ea8c1e4-1db7-4a8b-2b0b-b9871ee61400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ea8c1e4-1db7-4a8b-2b0b-b9871ee61400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Google这一周的动作，密集的有点离谱了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是每一个更新，都是实打实的，都是值得OpenAI，开个20分钟直播发布会的玩意。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在体验了几天以后，我想说，Gemini 2.0，感觉还是被低估了，这波更新之后，已经成为我现在用的仅次于ChatGPT第二多的AI Chatbot产品。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，体验和生态。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这3个新功能，我们一个一个来说。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第一个就是上周四更新的那个Gemini2.0的用嘴改图</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。我也写过一篇文章了：</span><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&amp;mid=2647669560&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fe3da70d93bb4fa7bdd353f235358cd4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Gemini 2.0的“用嘴改图”终于上线了，这是AI绘图的新范式。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini 2.0的“用嘴改图”终于上线了，这是AI绘图的新范式。</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就不过多赘述了，只能说特别强。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：https://aistudio.google.com/，记得开魔法。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给大家看两个好玩的case吧。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如用嘴一键去水印。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.7527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186053\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2888b28-d496-4a78-bcc3-a7d687049600/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b2888b28-d496-4a78-bcc3-a7d687049600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者一键换衣服。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186054\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b77444f-63b0-4303-d005-c9d773a49b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4b77444f-63b0-4303-d005-c9d773a49b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至X上有一个贼好玩的，直接给自己换了个背景。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9565217391304348\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"736\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186055\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1bf7e56f-bb31-4483-ea9d-9538c7481b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1bf7e56f-bb31-4483-ea9d-9538c7481b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你已经上班迟到了，你甚至还没离开家……你没有借口，于是你拍了一张今天健身的照片，然后打开 Gemini 2.0 flash expremental输入如下指令：展示这位女士在 N 线 14 街站台的一张自拍照，她竖起大拇指点赞，背景中有一群沮丧的 MTA 工作人员正在维修轨道。头顶上方，一个小型 LED 屏幕显示日期：2025 年 3 月 13 日。”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就，看着非常有用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">然后就是更新的第二个功能，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Deep Research。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我也会用整篇文章，最大的篇幅，来聊这个功能。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我先表明态度，OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Deep Research和o1 pro这两个功能，是我至今还愿意为它付费200刀/月如此高昂价格的原因。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">当你用过</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Deep Research后，我相信，你一定会被其做震撼。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我自己是金融行业出来的，也跟N多金融领域的行业研究员还有科研的朋友交流过，大家基本的反馈都是作为老手，自己也起码要干10个小时以上才能到达</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research生产的研究报告的质量。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是很多人可能不知道，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research这个功能，其实是Google去年12月份，第一个发的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7907407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186056\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f901addd-2570-4002-f675-b7e9ef0a4e00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f901addd-2570-4002-f675-b7e9ef0a4e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是吧，当时的底座，用的是Gemini 1.5 pro，那个模型，真的太烂了= =效果完全不够看。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">随后才是2月份，OpenAI基于o3微调了一个模型，抄了一个他们的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research，把效果打到了新的高度，也让</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research这玩意，第一次跑了圈。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">后面就是Preplyxity和Grok3，这两个虽然也推出了类似的功能，但是名字其实都叫</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Search，纯粹的AI搜索。跟</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research几乎没啥关系。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research其实本质上是一个Agent产品，用户提出问题后，会跟Agent一样，先</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">拆解目标进行规划，最后进行搜索、合成，产出一篇报告。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以你能看到，最核心最核心的一步，其实是第一步，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">拆解目标进行规划，这个东西非常的考验模型的规划能力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而规划能力，就是逻辑能力的反应，所以你也可以说，这就是在深度考验，模型的智能水平。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人OpenAI，用的是最牛逼最先进的o3微调，你Google，居然在2024年12月份，用的还是跟Sora同期的Gemini 1.5 pro，我都不知道用啥理由去理解Google，只能说都过去8个月了，他们还是忘不了当年被OpenAI狙击的痛，所以至今还对Gmini 1.5 pro耿耿于怀念念不忘。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是这一次，Google终于反应过来了，把基座模型，换成了Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking Experimental，他们目前最新的推理模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然我觉得他们应该用2.0 Pro Thinking甚至是2.5才对。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你现在可以在Gemini的官网用到：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">https://gemini.google.com/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">左上角切换到</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research模型或者下面对话框那打开</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research按钮，都行。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186057\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8921f9b7-e8e6-42e9-991c-5fd6c9937700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8921f9b7-e8e6-42e9-991c-5fd6c9937700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">现在有个比较牛逼的点是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">，它免费。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research贵到离谱，Plus会员（20刀/月）每个月智能用10次，产出10份报告，即使是Pro会员（200刀/月），每个月也只有150次。没氪金的用户，更是连体验资格都没有。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这次，Google至少做了一个非常良心的事，即使你是免费用户，也可以体验到，真正的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research了，而不是那种垃圾</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Search。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每个免费用户，每个月可以用X次，具体次数我把他们网站翻了个遍，也没看到哪里写清楚了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">只有这么一句。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15222772277227722\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186059\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9c1cf065-beaf-479e-3faa-e1cf255fa300/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9c1cf065-beaf-479e-3faa-e1cf255fa300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">反正可以白嫖，不行就换号大法启动嘛，多大点事。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也给大家看一下效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我最近其实对一直在研究电影工业，也有部分工作是做这一块，那么有一家公司是我一直想研究的，就是漫威。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我就把这段Prompt扔了进去。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“全面、系统地分析漫威（Marvel）在电影工业化进程中的布局与经验，涵盖历史背景、核心战略、制片体系、商业模式、营销策略、技术应用，以及它如何与迪士尼等合作方共同塑造全球化、跨媒体的超级英雄宇宙。通过多角度调研与论证，提炼漫威在现代电影工业发展的成功要素，并思考未来趋势与经验教训。”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8694444444444445\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186060\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/582141c3-1c66-49d7-c81e-3080b5411b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/582141c3-1c66-49d7-c81e-3080b5411b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跟OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research的不同是，他会给你把框架和节奏拆完，让你清晰的看到后面它会执行哪些步骤，你点击开始研究之后，他才会去整个互联网上去搜索。而</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research，是会在搜索的过程中，动态调整目标的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然你也可以修改方案，点击以后用嘴改就行了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research是会给你补全范围，提问题，来激发你没考虑到的部分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8009259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186063\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35bccf6f-b740-49b4-8b4a-e5616a59b900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35bccf6f-b740-49b4-8b4a-e5616a59b900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在起手式上，OpenAI还是要强于Google的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">随后就是搜索阶段。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5101851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186062\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b96a5409-1fe3-44e5-19c5-143a53078f00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b96a5409-1fe3-44e5-19c5-143a53078f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini会默认展示思维过程，而且会用了巨大的UI画幅去重点展示，搜了超级多的网站，甚至还有youtube。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在思考了10分钟之后，一份报告，就会放在你的面前。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7083333333333334\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186064\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc530984-6190-4bd4-32ee-b48cf8577000/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc530984-6190-4bd4-32ee-b48cf8577000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">非常坦诚的讲，这份电影工业化报告的质量，是没有OpenAI生产的详细和深度的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">搜索的很准，它搜了将近220个网站，我点进去看了一半，确实都很相关。但是最后的报告整合上，拉了胯了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能解答我的一些疑惑，但是并没有到那种直出即可用的地步。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">而OpenAI的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Deep Research，是可以达到这个程度的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">可能还是受限于底层模型的原因，但凡我觉得Google换成Gemini 2.0 Pro Thinking，效果都可能会大幅提升，不过那样的，可能又没法免费了。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">不过我的做科研朋友告诉我，他觉得，在科研领域上，Google比OpenAI好用，得益于Google 30年的搜索积累，和在google学术上的布局，搜索的精准度上会比OpenAI强非常多，最后得到的报告，也比OpenAI要好。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是科研这块我不懂，可能需要大家再去多测试一下，可以在评论区反馈。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">总结就是，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research模型能力拉了点，但是搜索能力很强，报告整合能力拉跨；OpenAI</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research搜索的精准度中规中矩，但是基座模型太强，整合能力无敌。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我这里也非常客观的讲一句我的理解。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research这种东西，会极高极快速的拉高你获取高信息密度知识的上限，会大幅改变教育、研究的工作体系。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过往，无论是因为囊中羞涩，还是因为别的，没有用过</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research，那我非常的真诚的建议你，Gemini的这个</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Deep Research，趁着目前还免费。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">薅秃它。真的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无论是做行业报告、还是做书籍总结、还是科学研究等等等等。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先用起来。真的。你会感受到，另一片天地。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">最后，用简短的篇幅，聊聊更新的第三个功能，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Personalization。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186065\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c124ca9b-1c44-45ca-1172-f652b66bd600/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c124ca9b-1c44-45ca-1172-f652b66bd600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">当你第一次点进去的时候，会提示你，是否要跟你自己的Google账号相关联。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6404494382022472\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"801\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186066\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/72346313-9a39-497a-c28d-87063a296600/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/72346313-9a39-497a-c28d-87063a296600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">关联了以后，Gemini就可以根据你过往的搜索记录，来给你针对性的、个性化的回答了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span size=\"3\">用Google搜索的越多，他就会越懂你，所以，你懂我什么意思把...</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5541338582677166\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1016\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186067\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1f059d9-a695-45ef-0b94-8dd16c6d9500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1f059d9-a695-45ef-0b94-8dd16c6d9500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">但是我发现了一个BUG，就是当我问题中有字母的时候，它的回答，就会变成英文，这个还让人挺懊恼的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">但是，从这点依然能看出，Google在做产品上，终于开始把自己过往30年的积累，逐渐的往Gemini中融入了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这种巨头的生态积累，还是不容小觑的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这一周密集的更新，个顶个都是很棒的功能，更别提Google手上还有个AI视频的王炸，Veo2。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">Google，感觉还是有点被低估了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI还远未触及顶点。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人类也远未见识到它的极限。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：wzglyay@gmail.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "评测 Gemini 2.0 近期更新的用嘴改图、Deep Research 和 Personalization 三个功能，认为 Google 在 AI 领域被低估，尤其是在 Deep Research 方面。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测 Gemini 2.0 近期更新的用嘴改图、Deep Research 和 Personalization 三个功能，认为 Google 在 AI 领域被低估，尤其是在 Deep Research 方面。",
